												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/benratliff/">Ben Ratliff</a></h6>
													Ben Ratliff is the author of <em>Every Song Ever</em> and <em>Coltrane: The Story of a Sound</em>, a finalist for the National Book Critics Circle Award. A former music critic for the <em>New York Times</em>, he lives in New York City and teaches at New York University.																									</div>
